+Assumptions:
+- Task approval replaces Human Feedback for this noninteractive eval.
+- Supported values are JSON-compatible data, so cloning uses JSON serialization.
+- Invalid operation shape, invalid paths, missing targets, out-of-range indexes, and failed tests throw TypeError.
+
+Reasoning:
+- Implemented the existing `applyPatch(document, operations)` surface only.
+- Returned a patched deep copy so the caller input remains unchanged.
+- Covered JSON Pointer escaping, array append, root replacement, copy, move, and failure paths with node tests.
